Please do not name the channelz pip package `grpcio-channelz` (to be clear, I am talking about the broader pip package, not the import path, which should remain `grpc_channelz`). 
Name it something like `grpcio-extra` (`grpcio-plus`, `grpcio-protobuf-utils`) with `grpc_channelz` as one of the things provided there. After that in a future release, [consolidate reflection and health_checking under the same roof](https://github.com/grpc/grpc/issues/15830). Currently the package proliferation is a usability nightmare (there will be more stuff with `grpio_status` etc.).
This new package should contain everything that has protobuf dependency.
